6 B. Except as provided in subsection C of this section, a person
7 shall not intentionally or knowingly:
8 1. Operate an unmanned aircraft over a critical infrastructure
9 facility if the unmanned aircraft is less than four hundred (400)
10 feet above ground level;
11 2. Allow an unmanned aircraft to make contact with a critical
